http://www.sohu.com/a/426064249_162522	44666
<p><span>来源：<span>新华社</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>
<p>2020-10-20 20:21</p>
<p><i><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201020/b82f535f9a0e466fbd2c6cf8a80a3220.jpeg" /></i></p>
<p>一条大河波浪宽 </p>
<p>风吹稻花香两岸 </p>
<p>……</p>
